      "span_text": "In general, the main advantages of FF include, among others, (i) particles production occurs under gentle conditions, which makes it suitable for labile compound encapsulation, (ii) it is able to predict the final particle size controlling the particle size distribution, and (iii) it is possible to scale up the rate production when multiple parallel devices are operated  ."
